'''疾病管理廳'''（{{kor|k=질병관리청|hj=疾病管理廳}}，{{lang-en|Korea Disease Control and Prevention Agency, KDCA}}）是[[大韩民国|大韩民国]][[保健福祉部|保健福祉部]]所屬機構，負責[[慢性病|慢性病]]、[[傳染病|傳染病]]、[[罕見疾病|罕見疾病]]的預防、調查、檢疫，並進行各項試驗研究，進而改善韓國人民健康。該機構成立於2004年1月19日<ref name="成立" />，位於[[忠清北道|忠清北道]][[清州市|清州市]][[兴德区|兴德区]]{{Link-ko|五松邑|오송읍}}五松衛生技術行政綜合大樓<ref>{{Cite web | url = http://www.ktv.go.kr/content/view?content_id=356997 | title = 식약청 등 다음달부터 오송 이전 시작 | language = ko | publisher = [[国民放送|国民放送]] | date = 2010-10-20 | accessdate = 2020-07-02 | archive-date = 2020-07-03 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200703150843/http://www.ktv.go.kr/content/view?content_id=356997 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="五松生命科學園區竣工典禮">{{Cite web | url = http://www.yakup.com/news/?mode=view&nid=137541 | title = 오송 보건의료행정타운 "세계 7위 HT 강국 도약" | language = ko | author = 임채규 | publisher = Yakup.com | date = 2010-12-20 | accessdate = 2020-07-10 | archive-date = 2020-07-11 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200711070407/http://www.yakup.com/news/?mode=view&nid=137541 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

2020年5月10日，總統[[文在寅|文在寅]]於就職3周年演說<ref name="就職演說全文">{{Cite news | url = https://www.koreatimes.co.kr/www/nation/2020/05/356_289260.html | title = [FULL TEXT] President Moon's special address | language = ko | publisher = [[韓國時報|韓國時報]] | date = 2020-05-10 | accessdate = 2020-07-06 | archive-date = 2020-07-06 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200706054949/https://www.koreatimes.co.kr/www/nation/2020/05/356_289260.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>時表示為強化應對包括[[2019冠状病毒病|2019冠状病毒病]]在內的各項傳染病，將原隸屬於[[保健福祉部|保健福祉部]]的疾病管理本部升格為獨立的疾病管理廳<ref>{{Cite news | url = https://www.ettoday.net/news/20200510/1710762.htm | title = 文在寅就職3周年！誓言打造全球第一防疫國　以經濟突破「後新冠時代」 | language = zh-tw | author = 陳宛貞 | publisher = [[ETtoday新聞雲|ETtoday新聞雲]] | date = 2020-05-10 | accessdate = 2020-07-06 | archive-date = 2020-07-06 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200706054953/https://www.ettoday.net/news/20200510/1710762.htm | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="질병관리청2">{{Cite news | url = https://www.seoul.co.kr/news/newsView.php?id=20200706016002 | title = 정은경도 갸웃한 ‘질병관리청 소속 보건연구원’… 최선일까 | language = ko | author = 강국진 | publisher = 서울신문 | date = 2020-07-05 | accessdate = 2020-07-05 | archive-date = 2020-07-07 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200707082005/https://www.seoul.co.kr/news/newsView.php?id=20200706016002 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="韓聯社" >{{Cite news | url = https://cn.yna.co.kr/view/ACK20200603001000881?section=politics/index | title = 韩国疾病管理本部将升格为疾病管理厅 | language = zh-cn | publisher = [[韓聯社|韓聯社]] | date = 2020-06-03 | accessdate = 2021-06-21 | archive-date = 2020-07-06 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200706102912/https://cn.yna.co.kr/view/ACK20200603001000881?section=politics%2Findex | dead-url = no }}</ref>，並於9月12日正式運作<ref name="KDCA成立" >{{Cite news | url = https://www.hani.co.kr/arti/area/capital/961196.html | title = 질병관리본부, 12일 ‘질병관리청’ 승격…정원 42% 늘어 | language = ko | author = 송경화 | publisher = [[韓民族日報|韓民族日報]] | date = 2020-09-08 | accessdate = 2021